						<p>Broken slab in front of the Ādi-Śankara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Bukkarāya 14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>In this fragmentary inscription Bukkarāya is mentioned and all other details are lost. It is in 14th century A.D. characters. Probably Bukkarāya made some grants, the details of which are lost.</p>						

